---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../utils/paths';

const contactHref = withBase('contact/');
---

<Layout title="Layanan AI Automation - my-aicustom.com">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?w=1200" alt="Layanan transformasi AI" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-screen-xl relative z-10 text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide bg-white/10 rounded-full">Solusi End-to-End</span>
        <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold">Layanan AI untuk Skalakan Operasional Bisnis Anda</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-200">Mulai dari otomasi proses hingga analitik prediktif, kami membantu mengimplementasikan AI yang memberikan dampak nyata.</p>
        <a href={contactHref} class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 bg-white rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100">Jadwalkan Konsultasi Gratis</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-screen-xl">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Paket Layanan Kami</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Setiap solusi dirancang modular agar mudah disesuaikan dengan kebutuhan operasional dan industri Anda.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="flex flex-col h-full p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?w=600" alt="Chatbot AI" class="w-full h-44 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Chatbot AI Custom</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Bangun asisten virtual yang memahami konteks bisnis Anda dan terintegrasi dengan CRM maupun kanal digital lainnya.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• NLP bilingual & integrasi WhatsApp</li>
            <li>• Knowledge base dinamis</li>
            <li>• Dashboard monitoring percakapan</li>
          </ul>
          <a href={contactHref} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Diskusikan Solusi</a>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col h-full p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?w=600" alt="Business Process Automation" class="w-full h-44 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Business Process Automation</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Otomatisasi alur kerja manual seperti input data, validasi dokumen, hingga pelaporan rutin untuk menghemat jam kerja tim.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• Audit proses end-to-end</li>
            <li>• Integrasi dengan ERP/CRM</li>
            <li>• Dashboard performa real-time</li>
          </ul>
          <a href={contactHref} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pelajari Implementasi</a>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col h-full p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483478550801-ceba5fe50e8e?w=600" alt="AI Analytics" class="w-full h-44 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">AI Analytics & Insights</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Eksplorasi data dengan model prediktif dan dashboard visual untuk mendukung pengambilan keputusan yang cepat dan akurat.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• Data pipeline & governance</li>
            <li>• Model prediksi custom</li>
            <li>• Visualisasi interaktif</li>
          </ul>
          <a href={contactHref} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Minta Demo Insight</a>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col h-full p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520607162513-77705c0f0d4a?w=600" alt="Computer vision" class="w-full h-44 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Computer Vision & OCR</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Automasi verifikasi dokumen, inspeksi visual, dan quality control dengan model vision akurasi tinggi.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• Model deteksi custom</li>
            <li>• Integrasi kamera industrial</li>
            <li>• Pelaporan otomatis</li>
          </ul>
          <a href={contactHref} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Bahas Kebutuhan Anda</a>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col h-full p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737604893-d14cc237f11d?w=600" alt="Pelatihan AI" class="w-full h-44 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Training & Change Management</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Bimbing tim Anda agar siap mengadopsi solusi AI melalui workshop interaktif dan pendampingan implementasi.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• Workshop onsite/online</li>
            <li>• Playbook adopsi AI</li>
            <li>• Support pasca implementasi</li>
          </ul>
          <a href={contactHref} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Rancang Program</a>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col h-full p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=600" alt="Strategi AI" class="w-full h-44 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">AI Strategy & Advisory</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Definisikan roadmap AI perusahaan, prioritas inisiatif, dan tata kelola yang selaras dengan tujuan bisnis jangka panjang.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>• Assessment maturity AI</li>
            <li>• Business case & KPI</li>
            <li>• Blueprint implementasi</li>
          </ul>
          <a href={contactHref} class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Mulai Konsultasi</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-screen-xl">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center mx-auto">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">Workflow</span>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Cara Kami Bekerja</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Pendekatan kolaboratif untuk memastikan setiap implementasi AI memberikan ROI yang terukur.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">01. Assessment</span>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Discovery & Alignment</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Workshop untuk memahami target bisnis, constraint, dan kesiapan data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">02. Build</span>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prototyping & Iteration</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Kembangkan solusi secara agile dengan feedback loop yang cepat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">03. Scale</span>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Deploy & Enablement</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Roll-out terukur lengkap dengan dokumentasi, pelatihan, dan support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a href={contactHref} class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Mulai Diskusi Proyek</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
